# Schola

## What It Is
A Malaysian career guidance platform targeting students aged 13–19 (Form 1 through SPM leavers). Operates at schola.org.my in English and Bahasa Malaysia.

## Core Products
- **Job Guides** — bilingual (EN/BM) career profiles with salary, education pathways, demand data, expert quotes, and knowledge tests
- **[[ola-chatbot]]** — AI career exploration assistant embedded in the platform
- **Social media comment classifier** — automated pipeline to classify audience engagement (see [[comment-taxonomy-pipeline]])

## Social Media Presence
- Instagram: @schola.my
- TikTok: active (TikTok Research API in use)
- Threads: planned Phase 2

## Language Strategy
All content is produced in both English and Bahasa Malaysia. Ola responds in the user's language and matches Manglish when appropriate.

## Industry Coverage
At minimum: Banking & Finance (Actuary guide confirmed). Broader coverage inferred from guide architecture.

